edu.jsu.mcis

Class Argument

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.jsu.mcis.Argument

  • public class Argument
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds information about the argument. It also contains the enumerated type that defines the data type for each argument.
    Supported data types include String, boolean, float, and int.
